<h2>Our Mission</h2>

<p>
Iransap is an independent initiative focused on building awareness,
knowledge, and professional networks around SAP technologies
within the Iranian technology community.
</p>

<p>
While international regulatory limitations currently restrict
direct collaboration with many global enterprise software providers,
there is strong interest among Iranian engineers and businesses
to learn and prepare for future participation in the global
enterprise technology ecosystem.
</p>

